{"tid":1179991,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"求救 一人一個可以舒緩急性腸胃炎既方法","createTime":"2019-05-31T13:25:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T14:40:48.000Z","uid":213101,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"1a1895b4920cbc3ed1ba7e1bbaf16e33d12d89f0","tid":1179991,"uid":213101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T13:25:53.000Z","msg":"琴日晏就食完米線 跟住夜晚食大排檔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n返到屋企就開始唔舒服 <br />\n兩三點自己彈起身 手腳麻痹 好似休克咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食完藥之後 5分鐘即刻嘔 係全部都嘔晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住開始肚柯 依家都仲柯緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  肚勁辛苦<br />\n要長期訓係張床先舒服少少<br />\n一行黎行去條氣勁唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n平時兩三個月都會有一次<br />\n但今次係手腳麻痹<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9e51ccc83333aa860f462abf9eb26c15b300f55","tid":1179991,"uid":213101,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T13:31:27.000Z","msg":"推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7bdc22cd9c96f7f0e3d81e4466bf19e4119cb3c","tid":1179991,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T13:34:48.000Z","msg":"重有無肚屙呀？"},{"pid":"57784031332d3916eb3c7105ee79150f37c33b41","tid":1179991,"uid":231886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T13:38:18.000Z","msg":"起我底，我岩岩柯左3日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b0e98357e0bcbb1fbc3f0032672370eca274b30","tid":1179991,"uid":231886,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T13:39:30.000Z","msg":"我呢3日大量飲水 寶礦力，你柯清曬就無事。千奇唔好去食止柯藥，拖得更耐。"},{"pid":"1d07f7600228d949e06b45138d44816c9b57c82e","tid":1179991,"uid":176802,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T13:39:42.000Z","msg":"打飛機"},{"pid":"5a4415